---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Testimonials from "../../../components/Testimonials";
import GetQuote from "../../../components/buttons/GetQuote.astro";
import ButtonScrollTop from "../../../components/buttons/ButtonScrollTop";
---

<style>
  .custom-background {
    background:
      linear-gradient(hsla(250, 75%, 5%, 0.5), rgba(6, 3, 21, 0.5)),
      url("/img/auction.webp") center center no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
  }
</style>


<Layout title="Auto Auction Shipping | Cayad Autro Transport"
content="">
  <div
    class="container-fluid flex flex-col items-center justify-center custom-background h-[60vh]"
  >
    <div class="w-[80%]">
      <h2
        class="text-white text-[4rem] xs:text-[1.8rem] sm:text-[1.8rem] font-bold"
      >
      Cayad ships vehicles from any auto auction.
      </h2>
      <h1 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold">
        We offers nationwide vehicle shipping across the U.S, accommodating all types of vehicles from any auction.
      </h1>
      <GetQuote />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 flex justify-center mb-8">
    <Testimonials title="Our Customer Say" client:load />
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
          Transport vehicles quickly and conveniently
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base mt-8">
          You are not just running an auction business, you are orchestrating
          hundreds of moves with such precision that top-rated surgeons would be
          impressed. One wrong move, miscommunication or delay and your
          business, as well as those of your buyers and sellers, could cost you
          money. That is why having the right transportation and specialist
          partner on your team is critically important.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base mt-8">
          Cayad Auto Transport has the technology and carrier resources to
          efficiently transport inbound and outbound vehicles for your auto
          auction operation.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-[40%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%]">
        <img
          src="/img/auto-auctions2.jpeg"
          class="rounded-xl w-full h-[100%]"
          alt="car shipping from auction"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex flex-col justify-between"
    >
      <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
        Transport vehicles quickly and conveniently
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base text-[#555] mt-4">
        Cayad can handle moves for any type of auction operationâ€”large physical
        auctions and online marketplaces, as well as independent and specialty
        auto auctions.
      </p>

      <p class="text-base text-[#555] mt-4">
        The auction team at Cayad understands that moving vehicles your way is
        the best way. Our services can complement your specific processes,
        following your hours of operation, regulations, gate pass procedures and
        vehicle location strategy.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base text-[#555] mt-4">
        We provide reliable pricing though our market-driven pricing engine,
        which analyzes historical trends, seasonality and surplus vs. demand to
        generate rates. We can also customize set pricing to fit your exact
        needs or provide contract pricing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[40%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%]">
        <img src="/img/dealership_circle_3.avif" class="rounded-xl" />
      </div>
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
          Single-unit move expertise
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base mt-8">
          We are the leader in single-unit moves and have the capacity to pickup
          or deliver vehicles just around the corner or more than 140 miles
          away. Whether you have a single vehicle to transport or one hundred,
          Cayads scalable capacity provides quick response with skilled vehicle
          handling and average pickup and transit times lower than the
          competition.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
          Nationwide pickup and delivery coverage
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base mt-8">
          Our vetted network of more than 15,000 carriers includes small,
          independent owner operators in markets from coast to coast. All
          carriers are screened, monitored and evaluated on a regular basis to
          ensure they meet insurance and safety requirements. They understand
          and respect the strict security protocols that must be followed in the
          auction industry.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-[40%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%]">
        <img src="/img/dealership_circle_5.webp" class="rounded-xl" alt="auto transport from dealership usa map 2"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[40%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%]">
        <img src="/img/dealership_circle_6.webp" class="rounded-xl" alt="car shipping from dealership usa map"/>
      </div>
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
          Technologies for speed and efficiency
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base mt-8">
          If you leverage auction software, we can seamlessly integrate with
          your system so you can quickly book orders and gain visibility into
          all movements, all on one platform. To speed unloading, improve
          accuracy and reduce the billing cycle, Cayad uses electronic proof of
          delivery (ePOD) and digital bill of lading (BOL).
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col xs:flex-col sm:flex-col items-center h-max w-full">
    <div class="w-[80%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%] xs:p-4 sm:p-4">
      <h2
        data-aos="fade-up"
        class="text-[2.5rem] xs:text-xl text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold"
      >
        Cayad is the ideal auto transport partner for dealerships
      </h2>

      <div
        class="grid mt-8 grid-cols-2 xs:grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 w-full gap-6"
      >
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.3s"
        >
          <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold">
            Experience
          </h5>
          <p class="py-4" style="text-align: justify;">
            Cayad Auo Transport has been moving cars one at a time since 2007.
            We average 400 shipments per day, including weekends, and can safely
            handle your local and long-distance moves.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.5s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold">
              Technology
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4" style="text-align: justify;">
              We leverage the latest technology to make car shipping easier and
              more convenient for our customers. Our innovation and service
              drive progress for our customers operations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.7s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold">
              Innovation
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4" style="text-align: justify;">
              Our priority on product and service innovations fuels our
              customers success. We were experts checking the market for get
              the best rates.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.9s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 text-xl py-4 text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold">
              Responsiveness
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4" style="text-align: justify;">
              With our 15,000+ carrier network and teams of experienced
              transportation and customer service experts, Nep Auto Tansport has
              the capacity and expertise to respond to your needs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex flex-col justify-between"
    >
      <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
        How Cayad can help your auction business
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base text-[#555] mt-4">
        <span class="text-[#555] font-bold">End-to-end solutions:</span>
        Taking a consultative approach, we will work with your inside sales reps,
        operations team and business leaders to make recommendations to improve service
        levels and transparency. We can benchmark our costs and service capabilities
        against your current providers to prove our value.
      </p>

      <p class="text-base text-[#555] mt-4">
        <span class="text-[#555] font-bold">Preferred transporter:</span>
        Whether for one or all of your locations, Cayad will deliver first-class
        service, reducing your stress and maximizing your time to focus on growing
        your business. We can be your one-stop solution for cars, trucks, motorcycles
        and powersports, with the trailer options and equipment required to handle
        recreational vehicles, luxury or collector cars and inoperable vehicles.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base text-[#555] mt-4">
        <span class="text-[#555] font-bold">Augment established carriers:</span>
        Cayad routinely handles long-distance moves and can extend the reach of your
        local carriers with our nationwide network of vetted carriers. The right
        partner will work in harmony with your auction operations and your established
        carriers to extend reach and increase efficiency to your operation.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="w-full flex mb-8 flex-col items-center xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-0 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-0 mx-auto overflow-hidden px-0"
  >
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-4 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-4 py-10 px-0"
    >
      <h2 class="text-4xl text-[#19171fd2] font-medium mb-10">
        Why should you choose Cayad Auto Transport for auto auction shipping?
      </h2>
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 xs:grid-cols-1 gap-10"
      >
        <div class="wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img src="/img/dollar.png" class="w-24 h-20 mb-2" alt="auto transport from auction dollar logo"/>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">Competitive Prices</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                At Cayad Auto Transport, we understand the importance of getting
                a quality service at an affordable price. Our highly competitive
                prices ensure that you get the best value for your money. We
                work hard to provide transparent and surprise-free rates,
                without compromising the quality of our service.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img src="/img/easy.png" class="w-24 h-20 mb-2" alt="car transport from auction easy logo"/>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">Ease of shipping</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                We take pride in offering a hassle-free vehicle shipping
                process. From the moment you contact us to the delivery of your
                car at the final destination, we take care of all the details.
                Our highly trained staff will guide you through the entire
                process, ensuring that everything is fast and efficient. With
                Cayad Auto Transport, you can have peace of mind knowing that
                your vehicle is in good hands.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
            <img src="/img/call.png" class="w-24 h-24 mb-2" alt="auto shipping from auctions call logo"/>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">Personalized assistance</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                We recognize that every customer and every car shipment is
                unique. That's why our team of car transportation experts is
                available to provide personalized assistance at every stage of
                the process. Whether you need additional information, shipping
                status updates, or any other inquiries, our friendly staff will
                be delighted to assist you. Your satisfaction is our top
                priority.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-[95%] wow"
          data-aos="fade-right"
          data-aos-delay="100"
          style="min-height: 400px;"
        >
          <div class="h-full">
            <img
              src="/img/auction.webp"
              class="object-cover rounded-xl w-full h-full"
              alt="auto auction transport"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <ButtonScrollTop client:load />
</Layout>